    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>mayo </strong>with the <strong>remaining grated garlic</strong> (don't like raw garlic? Go easy!) and the <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>aioli</strong></p>",
